	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I vote for having 3 layers, one for sprites with no priority over the background, the background, and sprites with priority over the background.<br /><br />Then when you swivel the camera you can see all the layers better, this will provide some &quot;depth information&quot; of sorts that the video noted was lacking.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


