		<br />
	</div><br /><br />The wireframe box is a sprite object. Make the background with thickness = 3 units, and the sprites with thickness = 1 unit, and place the sprites at the &quot;middle&quot; of the background's Z axis. Good for games where sprites don't overlap with BG

		

